  "description": "Furnavia is Norway's largest annual furry convention. The organisation caters primarily to the furry community — a community with a common interest in anthropomorphic animals — expressed through art, literature, music, media, movies, crafts, and costumes.\n\nThe convention was founded in 2020 and held its first event in September 2023. It has grown steadily, with 2025 reaching roughly 444 paying attendees, and acts as a social gathering point for both Norwegian and international furries.",
